      <description>192000Z APR 26  NAVAREA IV 369/26.  1. NORTH AMERICAN ICE SERVICE (NAIS)     ICEBERG BULLETIN 200001Z APR.  2. WARNING! THE INTERNATIONAL ICE PATROL     IS EXPERIENCING REDUCED ICEBERG     RECONNAISSANCE. ALL ICEBERG LIMITS     REPORTED BELOW ARE ESTIMATED.     PLEASE NAVIGATE WITH CAUTION.  3. ICEBERG LIMIT ALONG TRACKLINE JOINING     46-55N 054-00W, 44-35N 052-00W,     44-15N 047-10W, 46-30N 044-15W,     50-00N 044-25W, 53-05N 047-55W,     59-00N 055-00W.  4. ESTIMATED ICEBERG LIMIT ALONG     </description>
